{"tid":890474,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（人山人海）新盤專輯︰尚悅．嶺開售首批152伙","createTime":"2018-11-05T10:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T10:06:17.000Z","uid":147097,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1f556bb45a13675fc08a7fb67df11308117b04ed","tid":890474,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtQgUh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtQgUh3.jpg&h=35665f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRApiKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRApiKL.jpg&h=f505d726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尚悅．嶺銷售現場 (代理提供)<br />\n<br />\n財經<br />\n<br />\n新盤專輯︰尚悅．嶺開售首批152伙<br />\n11月05日(一) 17:50   <br />\n尚悅．嶺銷售現場 (代理提供)<br />\n尚悅．嶺銷售現場 (代理提供)<br />\n恒基地產(00012)等旗下元朗尚悅．嶺今日(11月5日)開售首批152伙，現場所見，有不少準買家陸續到達現場。 <br />\n<br />\n據銷售安排，準買家於下午5至7時報到，認購2至4伙的A組買家率先揀樓，其後為選購1至2伙時段的B組買家。 <br />\n<br />\n是次發售的單位來自首兩張價單，單位實用面積介乎195至370方呎，當中60個單位折實售價低於400萬元，入場費逾317.67萬元，料為目前區內新盤最低。 <br />\n<br />\n當中1號及2號價單分別提供101伙與51伙，折實平均呎價約15,881元與15,569元。項目於昨日截票，市場消息透露，該盤共接獲逾450張入票，超額認購約兩倍。"},{"pid":"8d5faf0e6dc5a2acb3e2917e2e127f093d58ae3d","tid":890474,"uid":48679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"有人咩？<br />\n剩係見到狗"},{"pid":"b5cacadd959273e92b8cccc1921193aa14789518","tid":890474,"uid":8328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf522a9aae2132fa52ef68c5eceb2fe3fa24f047","tid":890474,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"任篤唔使爭 鐘意邊間就買邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2d8ea252774631639c35d0cbb347500c2e8e0e","tid":89047